{
  "video_id": "RtFFT4zjyTM",
  "title": "Talk about your death while you're still healthy | Michelle Knox",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Krystian Aparta"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12788.0,
      "end_time": 14554.0,
      "text": "To kick the bucket,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14578.0,
      "end_time": 16265.0,
      "text": "bite the dust,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 16289.000000000002,
      "end_time": 18412.0,
      "text": "cash in your chips,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 18436.0,
      "end_time": 21402.0,
      "text": "check out, depart, expire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 21426.0,
      "end_time": 22945.0,
      "text": "launch into eternity ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 24359.0,
      "end_time": 27542.0,
      "text": "These are all euphemisms we use in humor"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 27566.0,
      "end_time": 31153.0,
      "text": "to describe the one life event we are all going to experience:"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32597.0,
      "end_time": 33747.0,
      "text": "death."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 34759.0,
      "end_time": 37746.0,
      "text": "But most of us don&#39;t want to acknowledge death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37770.0,
      "end_time": 39644.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t want to plan for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 39668.0,
      "end_time": 43343.0,
      "text": "and we don&#39;t want to discuss it with the most important people in our lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44551.0,
      "end_time": 47682.0,
      "text": "I grew up in an Australian community where people got old or sick"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47706.0,
      "end_time": 48857.0,
      "text": "and passed away,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48881.0,
      "end_time": 50848.0,
      "text": "and only the adults attended the funeral."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 51495.0,
      "end_time": 54500.0,
      "text": "My parents would come home looking sad and drained,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54750.0,
      "end_time": 55860.0,
      "text": "but they didn&#39;t discuss it with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56306.0,
      "end_time": 59653.0,
      "text": "So I was ignorant to death and of the grieving process."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61210.0,
      "end_time": 63168.0,
      "text": "At 15, I got my invitation."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 63872.0,
      "end_time": 66230.0,
      "text": "A dear neighbor who was like an aunt to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66254.0,
      "end_time": 68103.0,
      "text": "died suddenly of a heart attack,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68127.0,
      "end_time": 70878.0,
      "text": "and I attended my first funeral and did my first reading."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72122.0,
      "end_time": 76900.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know the tightness in my chest and the dryness in my mouth was normal."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78376.0,
      "end_time": 81812.0,
      "text": "The celebrant got some of the facts wrong, and it made me really angry."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83270.0,
      "end_time": 85788.0,
      "text": "He talked about how she loved knitting."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88239.0,
      "end_time": 89390.0,
      "text": "Knitting."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 89414.0,
      "end_time": 90708.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90732.0,
      "end_time": 94792.0,
      "text": "He didn&#39;t mention that, at 75, she still mowed her own lawn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 94816.0,
      "end_time": 96943.0,
      "text": "built an amazing fish pond in her front yard"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 96967.0,
      "end_time": 98450.0,
      "text": "and made her own ginger beer."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 99390.0,
      "end_time": 101891.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m pretty sure \"keen knitter\""
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 101915.0,
      "end_time": 104231.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t what she would have chosen for her eulogy."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 104255.0,
      "end_time": 106238.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 106262.0,
      "end_time": 109563.0,
      "text": "I believe if we discuss death as part of day-to-day living,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 109587.0,
      "end_time": 112945.0,
      "text": "we give ourselves the opportunity to reflect on our core values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 112969.0,
      "end_time": 114913.0,
      "text": "share them with our loved ones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 114938.0,
      "end_time": 118602.0,
      "text": "and then our survivors can make informed decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 118626.0,
      "end_time": 122356.0,
      "text": "without fear or regret of having failed to honor our legacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 124316.0,
      "end_time": 128380.0,
      "text": "I am blessed to lead a wonderful, culturally diverse team,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 128620.0,
      "end_time": 129722.0,
      "text": "and in the last 12 months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 129746.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131865.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve lost five parents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 131889.0,
      "end_time": 133904.0,
      "text": "including my own father,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 133928.0,
      "end_time": 137896.0,
      "text": "and most recently, a former colleague who died at 41 from bowel cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 139392.0,
      "end_time": 141666.0,
      "text": "We started having open and frank conversations"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 141690.0,
      "end_time": 143245.0,
      "text": "about what we were experiencing."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 144270.0,
      "end_time": 146487.0,
      "text": "We talked about the practical stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 146511.0,
      "end_time": 148225.0,
      "text": "the stuff no one prepares you for:"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 149980.0,
      "end_time": 151136.0,
      "text": "dealing with government agencies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 151160.0,
      "end_time": 153214.0,
      "text": "hospitals, nursing homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 153238.0,
      "end_time": 154876.0,
      "text": "advanced care directives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 154900.0,
      "end_time": 156333.0,
      "text": "funeral directors"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 156357.0,
      "end_time": 159550.0,
      "text": "and extended family members,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 159790.0,
      "end_time": 160652.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 160676.0,
      "end_time": 163610.0,
      "text": "making decisions about coffins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 163860.0,
      "end_time": 164344.0,
      "text": "headstones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 164368.0,
      "end_time": 165850.0,
      "text": "headstone wording,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 165874.0,
      "end_time": 167820.0,
      "text": "headstone font size,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 167844.0,
      "end_time": 169436.0,
      "text": "all while sleep-deprived."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 170834.0,
      "end_time": 172708.0,
      "text": "We also discussed some of the issues"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 172732.0,
      "end_time": 175294.0,
      "text": "triggered by our various cultural backgrounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 175318.0,
      "end_time": 178240.0,
      "text": "and we realized there can be some significant differences"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 178480.0,
      "end_time": 180222.0,
      "text": "in how we honor the passing of a loved one."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 181504.0,
      "end_time": 184210.0,
      "text": "A great example of this is \"Sorry Business,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 184235.0,
      "end_time": 187138.0,
      "text": "practiced by Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander people."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 187895.0,
      "end_time": 189980.0,
      "text": "During Sorry Business,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 190400.0,
      "end_time": 193765.0,
      "text": "family members will take on specific roles and responsibilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 193789.0,
      "end_time": 196630.0,
      "text": "protocols such as limiting the use of photographs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 196654.0,
      "end_time": 198987.0,
      "text": "saying the name of the deceased,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 199110.0,
      "end_time": 201226.0,
      "text": "and holding a smoking ceremony"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 201250.0,
      "end_time": 205281.0,
      "text": "are all a sign of respect and allow for a peaceful transition of the spirit."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 206642.0,
      "end_time": 208602.0,
      "text": "These customs can be a complete contrast"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 208626.0,
      "end_time": 211940.0,
      "text": "to those we might practice in Western cultures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 211118.0,
      "end_time": 213285.0,
      "text": "where we would honor the memory of a loved one"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 213309.0,
      "end_time": 215895.0,
      "text": "by talking about them and sharing photographs."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 217312.0,
      "end_time": 219882.0,
      "text": "So my lesson from this last year is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 219906.0,
      "end_time": 225500.0,
      "text": "life would be a lot easier to live if we talked about death now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 225740.0,
      "end_time": 226335.0,
      "text": "while we&#39;re healthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 227660.0,
      "end_time": 230673.0,
      "text": "For most of us, we wait until we are too emotional,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 230697.0,
      "end_time": 232197.0,
      "text": "too ill"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 232221.0,
      "end_time": 233967.0,
      "text": "or too physically exhausted --"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 235269.0,
      "end_time": 236544.0,
      "text": "and then it&#39;s too late."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 237933.0,
      "end_time": 242670.0,
      "text": "Isn&#39;t it time we started taking ownership of our finale on this earth?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 243600.0,
      "end_time": 244266.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s get going."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 245581.0,
      "end_time": 247517.0,
      "text": "Do you know what you want when you die?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 248231.0,
      "end_time": 250522.0,
      "text": "Do you know how you want to be remembered?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 250834.0,
      "end_time": 252604.0,
      "text": "Is location important?"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 253500.0,
      "end_time": 255202.0,
      "text": "Do you want to be near the ocean"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 255226.0,
      "end_time": 256752.0,
      "text": "or in the ocean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 256776.0,
      "end_time": 258769.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 258793.0,
      "end_time": 262126.0,
      "text": "Do you want a religious service or an informal party,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 262150.0,
      "end_time": 264619.0,
      "text": "or do you want to go out with a bang,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 264643.0,
      "end_time": 266993.0,
      "text": "literally, in a firework?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 267170.0,
      "end_time": 268731.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 268755.0,
      "end_time": 271151.0,
      "text": "When it comes to death, there&#39;s so much to discuss,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 271175.0,
      "end_time": 273412.0,
      "text": "but I want to focus on two aspects:"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 273436.0,
      "end_time": 279310.0,
      "text": "why talking about and planning your death can help you experience a good death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 279550.0,
      "end_time": 281524.0,
      "text": "and then reduce the stress on your loved ones;"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 281548.0,
      "end_time": 284905.0,
      "text": "and how talking about death can help us support those who are grieving."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 285876.0,
      "end_time": 287524.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s start with planning."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 288241.0,
      "end_time": 290121.0,
      "text": "How many of you have a will?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 290146.0,
      "end_time": 291296.0,
      "text": "Put your hand up."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 291898.0,
      "end_time": 293972.0,
      "text": "Oh, this is fantastic."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 293996.0,
      "end_time": 298179.0,
      "text": "In Australia, 45 percent of adults over the age of 18"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 298203.0,
      "end_time": 300660.0,
      "text": "do not have a legal will."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 301133.0,
      "end_time": 303806.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re a little bit above average."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 303831.0,
      "end_time": 306177.0,
      "text": "This is a startling statistic"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 306201.0,
      "end_time": 309815.0,
      "text": "given that writing a will can actually be quite simple and inexpensive."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 310750.0,
      "end_time": 312846.0,
      "text": "So I started asking my friends and neighbors"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 312870.0,
      "end_time": 316770.0,
      "text": "and was really surprised to learn many of them don&#39;t have a will,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 316101.0,
      "end_time": 319280.0,
      "text": "and some couples don&#39;t realize they need individual wills."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 319627.0,
      "end_time": 323420.0,
      "text": "The usual explanation was, well, it&#39;s all going to go to my partner anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 324667.0,
      "end_time": 326494.0,
      "text": "So keep in mind that laws vary"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 326518.0,
      "end_time": 329335.0,
      "text": "from state to state and country to country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 329359.0,
      "end_time": 331517.0,
      "text": "but this is what happens in New South Wales"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 331541.0,
      "end_time": 334170.0,
      "text": "if you die without leaving a legal will."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 335621.0,
      "end_time": 338818.0,
      "text": "Firstly, a suitable administrator must be appointed"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 338843.0,
      "end_time": 341650.0,
      "text": "by the Supreme Court of New South Wales."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 341854.0,
      "end_time": 345270.0,
      "text": "Chances are this is someone who would never have met the deceased."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 345814.0,
      "end_time": 349225.0,
      "text": "That person is then responsible for arranging your funeral,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 349249.0,
      "end_time": 353900.0,
      "text": "collecting assets and distributing them after paying debts and taxes."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 354420.0,
      "end_time": 357250.0,
      "text": "And one of those debts will be the bill for their services."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 357462.0,
      "end_time": 359366.0,
      "text": "This is not someone who would have known"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 359391.0,
      "end_time": 362580.0,
      "text": "you want the four-foot wooden giraffe in your living room"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 362820.0,
      "end_time": 365537.0,
      "text": "to go to the person who helped you carry it halfway across the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 365561.0,
      "end_time": 367873.0,
      "text": "and yes, that&#39;s in my will."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 367898.0,
      "end_time": 369799.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 370251.0,
      "end_time": 372938.0,
      "text": "If you die leaving a spouse or a domestic partner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 372963.0,
      "end_time": 375782.0,
      "text": "then chances are they will receive your estate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 375806.0,
      "end_time": 378726.0,
      "text": "but if you are single, it&#39;s far more complicated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 378750.0,
      "end_time": 383306.0,
      "text": "as parents, siblings, half-siblings and dependents all come into play."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 384101.0,
      "end_time": 388455.0,
      "text": "And did you know that if you make a regular donation to charity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 388479.0,
      "end_time": 391394.0,
      "text": "that charity may have grounds to make a claim on your estate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 392511.0,
      "end_time": 395784.0,
      "text": "The most important thing to know is the bigger your estate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 395808.0,
      "end_time": 397698.0,
      "text": "the more complicated that will will be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 397722.0,
      "end_time": 399704.0,
      "text": "and the more expensive that bill."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 400882.0,
      "end_time": 404670.0,
      "text": "So if you don&#39;t have a will, I ask you ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 405406.0,
      "end_time": 407402.0,
      "text": "when else in your life"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 407426.0,
      "end_time": 410567.0,
      "text": "have you willingly given money to the government"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 410591.0,
      "end_time": 412290.0,
      "text": "when you didn&#39;t have to?"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 412530.0,
      "end_time": 414267.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 415682.0,
      "end_time": 419630.0,
      "text": "I lost my father in February to a progressive lung disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 419706.0,
      "end_time": 421506.0,
      "text": "When dad knew his death was imminent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 421530.0,
      "end_time": 422943.0,
      "text": "he had three clear wishes."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 423698.0,
      "end_time": 426150.0,
      "text": "He wanted to die at home;"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 426400.0,
      "end_time": 428569.0,
      "text": "he wanted to die surrounded by family;"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 428593.0,
      "end_time": 431674.0,
      "text": "and he wanted to die peacefully, not choking or gasping for air."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 433800.0,
      "end_time": 437183.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m pleased to say that my family were able to support dad&#39;s wishes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 437207.0,
      "end_time": 438814.0,
      "text": "and he achieved his goals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 438838.0,
      "end_time": 441817.0,
      "text": "and in that sense, he had a good death."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 442444.0,
      "end_time": 444206.0,
      "text": "He had the death he planned for."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 445538.0,
      "end_time": 447237.0,
      "text": "Because dad wanted to die at home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 447261.0,
      "end_time": 449405.0,
      "text": "we had to have some pretty tough conversations"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 449429.0,
      "end_time": 451133.0,
      "text": "and fill out a lot of paperwork."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 451853.0,
      "end_time": 456138.0,
      "text": "The questions on the forms cover everything from resuscitation to organ donation."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 457282.0,
      "end_time": 460393.0,
      "text": "Dad said, \"Take whatever organs you can use.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 461226.0,
      "end_time": 463289.0,
      "text": "This was upsetting to my mum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 463313.0,
      "end_time": 465738.0,
      "text": "as my dad&#39;s health was deteriorating rapidly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 465762.0,
      "end_time": 469273.0,
      "text": "and it was no longer the right time to talk about organ donation."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 470912.0,
      "end_time": 474198.0,
      "text": "I believe we need to discuss these issues when we are fit and healthy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 474222.0,
      "end_time": 476669.0,
      "text": "so we can take the emotion out of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 476694.0,
      "end_time": 479472.0,
      "text": "and then we can learn not just what is important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 479496.0,
      "end_time": 481970.0,
      "text": "but why it&#39;s important."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 482269.0,
      "end_time": 484729.0,
      "text": "So as part of my journey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 484753.0,
      "end_time": 489277.0,
      "text": "I started engaging my family and friends to find out their thoughts on death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 489301.0,
      "end_time": 491118.0,
      "text": "and how they wanted to be remembered."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 492406.0,
      "end_time": 496739.0,
      "text": "I discovered you can host a \"Death Over Dinner,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 496763.0,
      "end_time": 498722.0,
      "text": "or a \"Death Cafe,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 498747.0,
      "end_time": 501507.0,
      "text": "which is a great, casual way to introduce the topic ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 501531.0,
      "end_time": 503564.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 503588.0,
      "end_time": 505342.0,
      "text": "and gain some wonderful insight."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 505366.0,
      "end_time": 507610.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 507850.0,
      "end_time": 510744.0,
      "text": "Did you know that your body has to be legally disposed of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 510768.0,
      "end_time": 513332.0,
      "text": "and you can&#39;t just be shoved off a cliff"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 513356.0,
      "end_time": 515460.0,
      "text": "or set fire to in the backyard?"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 515700.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516303.00000000006,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 516327.0,
      "end_time": 518203.0,
      "text": "In Australia, you have three options."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 518227.0,
      "end_time": 520474.0,
      "text": "The two most common are burial and cremation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 520499.0,
      "end_time": 523538.0,
      "text": "but you can also donate your body to science."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 523562.0,
      "end_time": 526491.0,
      "text": "And I am pleased to report that innovation has touched"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 526515.0,
      "end_time": 528109.0,
      "text": "the world of corpse disposal."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 528133.0,
      "end_time": 529234.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 529258.0,
      "end_time": 531314.0,
      "text": "You can now opt for an eco-funeral."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 531338.0,
      "end_time": 533406.0,
      "text": "You can be buried at the base of a tree"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 533430.0,
      "end_time": 536233.0,
      "text": "in recycled cardboard or a wicker basket,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 536258.0,
      "end_time": 537900.0,
      "text": "and for those who love the ocean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 537924.0,
      "end_time": 540480.0,
      "text": "there are eco-friendly urns that will dissolve at sea."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 541448.0,
      "end_time": 544179.0,
      "text": "Personally, I plan to be cremated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 544203.0,
      "end_time": 546717.0,
      "text": "but given that I get seasick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 546741.0,
      "end_time": 548552.0,
      "text": "I can think of nothing worse"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 548576.0,
      "end_time": 551822.0,
      "text": "than having my ashes flung into a huge ocean swell."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 552735.0,
      "end_time": 555655.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve actually bought a plot in the rose garden next to my dad."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 556314.0,
      "end_time": 558266.0,
      "text": "I call it my investment property."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 558291.0,
      "end_time": 560751.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 560775.0,
      "end_time": 563900.0,
      "text": "But sadly, there&#39;s no tax deduction."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 563924.0,
      "end_time": 566161.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 566185.0,
      "end_time": 569534.0,
      "text": "So if you plan for your death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 569558.0,
      "end_time": 573654.0,
      "text": "then your survivors will know how to experience a healthy bereavement"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 573678.0,
      "end_time": 576781.0,
      "text": "without fear or guilt of having failed to honor your legacy."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 577866.0,
      "end_time": 580533.0,
      "text": "As part of my research, I&#39;ve been to seminars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 580557.0,
      "end_time": 583603.0,
      "text": "read books and talked to palliative care nurses."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 583627.0,
      "end_time": 584958.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ve come to understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 584982.0,
      "end_time": 588300.0,
      "text": "as a consequence of not talking about death,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 588325.0,
      "end_time": 590452.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t know how to be around grief."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 591591.0,
      "end_time": 594810.0,
      "text": "And on the flip side, if we talk about death more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 594834.0,
      "end_time": 599151.0,
      "text": "we will become more comfortable with the emotions we experience around grief."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 601556.0,
      "end_time": 603327.0,
      "text": "I discovered, this year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 603351.0,
      "end_time": 607224.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s actually a privilege to help someone exit this life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 607248.0,
      "end_time": 611111.0,
      "text": "and although my heart is heavy with loss and sadness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 611135.0,
      "end_time": 612659.0,
      "text": "it is not heavy with regret."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 613524.0,
      "end_time": 615517.0,
      "text": "I knew what dad wanted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 615541.0,
      "end_time": 618413.0,
      "text": "and I feel at peace knowing I could support his wishes."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 621570.0,
      "end_time": 624698.0,
      "text": "My dad&#39;s last 24 hours were in a peaceful coma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 624722.0,
      "end_time": 626730.0,
      "text": "and after days of around-the-clock care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 626754.0,
      "end_time": 629167.0,
      "text": "we had time to sit, hold his hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 629191.0,
      "end_time": 630475.0,
      "text": "and say goodbye."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 631494.0,
      "end_time": 634883.0,
      "text": "He passed away on a Monday morning just before breakfast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 634907.0,
      "end_time": 636574.0,
      "text": "and after the doctor came"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 636598.0,
      "end_time": 639214.0,
      "text": "and we waited for the funeral home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 639238.0,
      "end_time": 642984.0,
      "text": "I went into the kitchen, and I ate a big bowl of porridge."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 645410.0,
      "end_time": 648136.0,
      "text": "When I told some of my friends this, they were really shocked."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 648947.0,
      "end_time": 651985.0,
      "text": "\"How could you eat at a time like that?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 653164.0,
      "end_time": 656730.0,
      "text": "Well, I was hungry."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 656970.0,
      "end_time": 660787.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 660811.0,
      "end_time": 664764.0,
      "text": "You see, grief impacted my sleep and my ability to concentrate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 664788.0,
      "end_time": 668390.0,
      "text": "but it never impacted my stomach. I was always hungry."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 668630.0,
      "end_time": 669247.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 669271.0,
      "end_time": 670881.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s different for all of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 670905.0,
      "end_time": 673626.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s really important that we acknowledge that."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 674698.0,
      "end_time": 677848.0,
      "text": "So if we don&#39;t talk about our death and the death of loved ones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 677873.0,
      "end_time": 682400.0,
      "text": "how can we possibly support a friend, a colleague, a neighbor"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 682280.0,
      "end_time": 683645.0,
      "text": "who is grieving?"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 683669.0,
      "end_time": 686678.0,
      "text": "How do we support someone who has lost someone suddenly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 686702.0,
      "end_time": 688605.0,
      "text": "like an accident or suicide?"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 689685.0,
      "end_time": 691145.0,
      "text": "We tend to avoid them ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 692359.0,
      "end_time": 694820.0,
      "text": "not because we don&#39;t care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 694844.0,
      "end_time": 696716.0,
      "text": "because we don&#39;t know what to say."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 697912.0,
      "end_time": 700564.0,
      "text": "We know as a friend we can&#39;t fix it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 700588.0,
      "end_time": 703183.0,
      "text": "we can&#39;t take away that pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 703207.0,
      "end_time": 706398.0,
      "text": "so we say things to fill that awkward silence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 706422.0,
      "end_time": 708119.0,
      "text": "sometimes things we regret saying."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 709532.0,
      "end_time": 710817.0,
      "text": "Examples would be:"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 713158.0,
      "end_time": 715174.0,
      "text": "\"At least he isn&#39;t suffering anymore.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 716673.0,
      "end_time": 718418.0,
      "text": "\"At least you&#39;ve got your memories.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 720215.0,
      "end_time": 723135.0,
      "text": "\"At least you don&#39;t have to pay for hospital parking anymore.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 723159.0,
      "end_time": 725255.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 725279.0,
      "end_time": 728400.0,
      "text": "Really, we don&#39;t need to say anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 728588.0,
      "end_time": 730480.0,
      "text": "We just need to be."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 731211.0,
      "end_time": 733550.0,
      "text": "Be patient,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 733790.0,
      "end_time": 735261.0,
      "text": "be understanding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 735285.0,
      "end_time": 736512.0,
      "text": "and be a listener."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 737672.0,
      "end_time": 740906.0,
      "text": "And if you can&#39;t be any of those things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 740930.0,
      "end_time": 745141.0,
      "text": "then please, be the person who makes the lasagna, the curry or the casserole,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 745165.0,
      "end_time": 747625.0,
      "text": "because your offerings will be greatly appreciated."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 747649.0,
      "end_time": 749212.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 749686.0,
      "end_time": 752280.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve been to 10 funerals in the last year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 752520.0,
      "end_time": 754220.0,
      "text": "one of which I helped arrange."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 754460.0,
      "end_time": 756264.0,
      "text": "They ran the full gamut:"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 756288.0,
      "end_time": 758749.0,
      "text": "a very solemn Greek Orthodox service,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 758773.0,
      "end_time": 761384.0,
      "text": "four Catholic requiem masses"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 761408.0,
      "end_time": 763670.0,
      "text": "and a garden party"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 763910.0,
      "end_time": 767528.0,
      "text": "where I made a toast while scattering my friend&#39;s ashes around her garden"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 767552.0,
      "end_time": 768877.0,
      "text": "with a soup ladle."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 768901.0,
      "end_time": 770426.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 770451.0,
      "end_time": 775850.0,
      "text": "I have carried, kissed, written on and toasted coffins with a shot of ouzo."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 775783.0,
      "end_time": 777359.0,
      "text": "I have worn all black,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 777383.0,
      "end_time": 780160.0,
      "text": "all color and a party dress."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 780184.0,
      "end_time": 782468.0,
      "text": "Despite the vast differences in sendoff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 782493.0,
      "end_time": 785150.0,
      "text": "despite me being at times out of my comfort zone"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 785390.0,
      "end_time": 787881.0,
      "text": "doing something I&#39;ve never done before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 787905.0,
      "end_time": 789865.0,
      "text": "I drew comfort from one thing --"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 790889.0,
      "end_time": 793873.0,
      "text": "knowing that this is what each person would have wanted."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 795187.0,
      "end_time": 796337.0,
      "text": "So what do I want?"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
